    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/51fcc534a1844ca0bfdc3bd315b3c903.avif?t=1744828738\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras_big/51fcc534a1844ca0bfdc3bd315b3c903.avif?t=1744828738 width=1170 height=141 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑猩猩记忆》是一款逻辑谜题和解决问题的游戏，既是对你的挑战，又能让你了解猴子的研究过程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您必须进行与猴子类似的神经测试，记住数字序列，并在数字隐形后对其顺序进行匹配！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/e95d3c218960eaa0f0d111c2093e3a57.poster.avif?t=1744828738\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/e95d3c218960eaa0f0d111c2093e3a57.webm?t=1744828738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/e95d3c218960eaa0f0d111c2093e3a57.mp4?t=1744828738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些测试基本上是记忆测试，黑猩猩接受训练，并且在它们所做的事情上表现出色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的挑战是在记忆和逻辑推理测试中表现更好，如下所示：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/3dfdf6d864222be904a97cf8f54bc396.poster.avif?t=1744828738\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/3dfdf6d864222be904a97cf8f54bc396.webm?t=1744828738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 全球排名中留下您的名字，并证明一只简单的猴子也无法胜过您！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谢谢，别忘了将游戏添加到您的愿望清单，以支持我们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/130d164b30bc70a74eea9fa8a7cbb22b.avif?t=1744828738\" width=616 height=273 /></span></p>",
